- File name: exchange.py
- Target path: /Users/user1/CODE/Tester/MetaGPT-2/humaneval_baseline
- The file should contain ONLY the function implementation above (no tests, no prints, no comments). No imports are needed.
- Ensure the file is written to disk successfully before reporting completion (overwrite if exists). After writing, read back the file to verify it contains only the function.
